registry_reads.data: Shows shortcuts to Web sites, network computers, and FTP sites.
Creates a new, empty folder in the folder you have open.
These links open other folders and take you quickly to useful places.
Transfers copies of the selected items to a public Web page so that you can share them with other people.
These tasks apply to the files and folders you select.
